## Cadena de ataque completa

```
Bundle JS publico -> GraphQL expuesto -> recon_token    [FLAG 1]
        |
OAuth authorize -> redirect_uri bypass -> access_token  [FLAG 2]
        |
PUT /users/me -> Mass Assignment -> rol admin           [FLAG 3]
        |
PDF renderer -> SSRF -> metadata AWS + clave publica    [FLAG 4]
        |
JWT HS256 forjado con clave publica -> vault            [FLAG 5]
```

